00:03:50.320 --> 00:03:51.280
I transmigrated into a

00:03:51.280 --> 00:03:54.540
cannon fodder death row inmate who dies right at the start.

00:04:09.520 --> 00:04:10.680
I feel pain,

00:04:10.800 --> 00:04:11.840
