00:05:56.560 --> 00:05:57.600
System Task.

00:05:58.600 --> 00:06:00.080
Monster: Yuantong.

00:06:00.200 --> 00:06:01.680
Weakness: Unknown.

00:06:01.840 --> 00:06:04.240
