00:06:12.360 --> 00:06:14.160
Only if you get out of this cell.

00:06:14.480 --> 00:06:16.480
Run as soon as you hear the rattle drum.

00:06:16.480 --> 00:06:17.760
Stop as soon as the drum stops.

00:06:17.760 --> 00:06:19.090
