00:07:31.800 --> 00:07:32.720
Damn.

00:07:33.400 --> 00:07:35.260
This is 'Red Light, Green Light'.

00:07:50.280 --> 00:07:51.800
If the drum beats an even number of times,

00:07:51.800 --> 00:07:53.800
both feet must not touch the ground.

00:08:14.880 --> 00:08:16.280
It kills according to a pattern.

00:08:16.280 --> 00:08:17.600
If the rattle drum beats an odd number of times,

00:08:17.600 --> 00:08:18.480
one foot must leave the ground.

00:08:18.480 --> 00:08:19.640
If the rattle drum beats an even number of times,

00:08:19.640 --> 00:08:21.640
both feet must not touch the ground.

00:08:22.840 --> 00:08:23.560
Even numbers.

00:08:23.560 --> 00:08:24.890
Don't touch the ground.

00:08:34.880 --> 00:08:35.840
This pose

00:08:35.960 --> 00:08:37.090
