00:13:05.320 --> 00:13:08.040
I became Su Ningxue, the Empress of the Great Qian.

00:13:08.040 --> 00:13:10.480
I remember the male lead in the book is named Han Qingyun.

00:13:10.480 --> 00:13:12.720
The plot is that he leads troops to attack Fengming City.

00:13:12.720 --> 00:13:14.080
I will die.

00:13:14.440 --> 00:13:16.970
And the Great Qian Dynasty will be destroyed.

00:13:17.120 --> 00:13:18.120
I...

00:13:18.120 --> 00:13:19.760
