00:13:20.160 --> 00:13:21.840
The kind that must die.

00:13:25.600 --> 00:13:26.400
Your Majesty.

00:13:26.440 --> 00:13:28.500
I have an important matter to report.

00:13:29.280 --> 00:13:31.560
This should be the Empress's sword servant, Su Wuhui.

00:13:31.560 --> 00:13:32.480
A top disciple of Tianji Pavilion,

00:13:32.480 --> 00:13:33.360
