00:13:43.560 --> 00:13:44.360
Your Majesty.

00:13:44.360 --> 00:13:46.600
A demon disaster occurred in the prison of Huaiyang City.

00:13:46.600 --> 00:13:47.920
Lin Mo, the prime suspect in the poisoned salt case,

00:13:47.920 --> 00:13:50.000
eliminated the demons all by himself.

00:13:50.000 --> 00:13:51.000
Lin Mo.

00:13:52.040 --> 00:13:53.520
I remember he was just cannon fodder in the book,

00:13:53.520 --> 00:13:55.040
who was quickly executed.

00:13:55.120 --> 00:13:56.560
How can cannon fodder be so powerful?

00:13:56.560 --> 00:13:58.080
Could it be...

00:13:58.960 --> 00:14:00.280
Bring that Lin Mo here immediately.

00:14:00.280 --> 00:14:00.880
Quick.

00:14:00.880 --> 00:14:01.400
Yes.

00:14:01.400 --> 00:14:02.200
Wait.

00:14:03.760 --> 00:14:06.240
You can be a little

00:14:06.240 --> 00:14:07.360
