00:14:10.600 --> 00:14:11.240
Yes.

00:14:13.760 --> 00:14:15.240
I need to survive first.

00:14:15.720 --> 00:14:17.600
I can't die here for no reason.

00:14:20.760 --> 00:14:22.160
Greetings, Your Majesty.

00:14:22.160 --> 00:14:24.020
The Empress Dowager summons you.

00:14:37.520 --> 00:14:39.400
Which way is the Empress Dowager's bedchamber?

00:14:39.400 --> 00:14:41.000
I don't know the way.

00:14:45.720 --> 00:14:46.520
It's bright here.

00:14:46.520 --> 00:14:47.520
