00:14:49.640 --> 00:14:51.400
Your Majesty, you went the wrong way.

00:14:51.400 --> 00:14:53.840
This is Dowager Consort Hua's bedchamber.

00:14:54.680 --> 00:14:56.000
I just want to see

00:14:56.000 --> 00:14:57.160
so late,

00:14:57.160 --> 00:14:58.880
