00:14:58.880 --> 00:14:59.760
Dowager Consort Hua.

00:14:59.760 --> 00:15:01.440
The one in the book who wants me dead,

00:15:01.440 --> 00:15:02.200
Dowager Consort Hua.

00:15:02.200 --> 00:15:03.320
Okay, got it.

00:15:03.320 --> 00:15:04.800
It's getting late.

00:15:04.800 --> 00:15:05.800
Please, Your Majesty,

00:15:05.800 --> 00:15:07.960
