00:16:23.720 --> 00:16:25.720
Greetings, Imperial Grandmother.

00:16:46.240 --> 00:16:48.520
Greetings, Imperial Grandmother.

00:16:49.000 --> 00:16:52.280
I wonder why you summoned me late at night.

00:16:52.280 --> 00:16:54.010
Is there something important?

00:16:55.280 --> 00:16:57.040
It's Ningxue.

00:16:57.440 --> 00:16:59.520
You are not asleep yet?

00:16:59.720 --> 00:17:00.840
Grandmother.

00:17:00.960 --> 00:17:03.280
Didn't you call me here?

00:17:04.400 --> 00:17:05.359
Yes.

00:17:05.720 --> 00:17:07.720
I called you here.

00:17:08.119 --> 00:17:09.960
Since the late emperor passed away,

00:17:09.960 --> 00:17:11.800
how many years has it been since you took the throne?

00:17:11.800 --> 00:17:13.400
To answer you, Grandmother,

00:17:13.640 --> 00:17:15.300
it's been less than two years.

00:17:15.359 --> 00:17:17.720
A ruler cannot be without an heir.

00:17:18.079 --> 00:17:20.200
Are you pregnant with a child now?

00:17:23.680 --> 00:17:25.040
Grandmother.

00:17:25.560 --> 00:17:28.079
Great Qian is now facing internal and external troubles.

00:17:28.079 --> 00:17:29.640
As the ruler,

00:17:29.840 --> 00:17:31.440
I should make every effort to govern well,

00:17:31.440 --> 00:17:32.600
rectify the administration,

00:17:32.600 --> 00:17:34.730
and develop the people's livelihood.

00:17:34.920 --> 00:17:36.880
Personal affairs

00:17:36.880 --> 00:17:38.210
can be discussed later.

00:17:38.360 --> 00:17:39.520
That's not appropriate.

00:17:39.520 --> 00:17:41.320
You have been on the throne for nearly two years

00:17:41.320 --> 00:17:43.520
and haven't given birth to an heir for the royal family.

00:17:43.520 --> 00:17:45.280
This is unreasonable.

00:17:45.680 --> 00:17:47.080
If word gets out,

00:17:47.160 --> 00:17:48.600
the civil and military officials might think

00:17:48.600 --> 00:17:51.680
the inner court has neglected our new emperor.

00:17:51.920 --> 00:17:53.780
We must hurry up with this matter.

00:17:54.520 --> 00:17:55.320
Yes.

00:17:55.320 --> 00:17:58.200
I will go back and look for candidates immediately.

00:18:01.280 --> 00:18:03.120
If only Ling Mo were here.

00:18:03.280 --> 00:18:04.360
I'd capture him as my male concubine.

00:18:04.360 --> 00:18:06.200
No need for such trouble.

00:18:06.440 --> 00:18:09.040
I have already chosen a candidate for you.

00:18:09.360 --> 00:18:10.720
Why not tonight?

00:18:10.720 --> 00:18:13.120
Get it done right here in the bedchamber.

00:18:13.440 --> 00:18:15.680
Let's keep things simple.

00:18:25.080 --> 00:18:26.480
My niece, Ningxue.

00:18:26.760 --> 00:18:28.280
Do you still remember me?

00:18:28.480 --> 00:18:29.480
He is...

00:18:29.600 --> 00:18:31.760
Grandmother's nephew whom I exiled,

00:18:33.040 --> 00:18:34.560
Xue Qian.

00:18:35.280 --> 00:18:36.800
You brought chaos to the palace

00:18:36.800 --> 00:18:38.200
and were exiled long ago.

00:18:38.240 --> 00:18:39.400
Why are you here?

00:18:39.880 --> 00:18:42.680
Because I missed my good niece,

00:18:42.960 --> 00:18:44.600
Su Ningxue.

00:18:45.680 --> 00:18:47.610
Grandmother, what does this mean?

00:18:48.080 --> 00:18:49.740
Are you trying to imprison me?

00:18:49.880 --> 00:18:52.320
How would I dare imprison Your Majesty?

00:18:52.920 --> 00:18:54.440
Just one night.

00:18:54.440 --> 00:18:55.080
We just need Your Majesty

00:18:55.080 --> 00:18:57.720
to conceive an heir of our Xue family.

00:18:57.720 --> 00:18:58.840
From then on,

00:18:58.840 --> 00:19:01.720
our Xue family will fully support you

00:19:01.760 --> 00:19:03.240
against the Chancellor,

00:19:03.240 --> 00:19:04.800
Lin Youtang.

00:19:06.760 --> 00:19:08.200
Such wild ambition.

00:19:08.880 --> 00:19:09.920
Guards!

00:19:09.920 --> 00:19:11.120
Where are the guards?

00:19:14.640 --> 00:19:15.400
Open the door!

00:19:15.400 --> 00:19:16.200
Let me out!

00:19:16.960 --> 00:19:17.640
Open it!

